tickets.subject: Sample ticket: Meet the ticket
tickets.description:
Hi Bita,

Emails, chats, voicemails, and tweets are captured in Zendesk Support as tickets. Start typing above to respond and click Submit to send. To test how an email becomes a ticket, send a message to support@bitacrosby.zendesk.com.

Curious about what your customers will see when you reply? Check out this video:
https://demos.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/202341799
